&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>to fuse the information from two pdfs we can multiply them together&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;h2 id="the-kalman-filter">
 The Kalman Filter
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#the-kalman-filter">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>卡尔曼滤波&lt;/strong> (Kalman Filter) 的工作步骤:&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>A Prediction Step and&lt;/li>
&lt;li>A Measurement Update Step&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h3 id="filter-equations">
 Filter Equations
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#filter-equations">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>
 &lt;div class="post-img-view">
